Package Default

Class CourseDBElement

java.lang.Object
Default.CourseDBElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<CourseDBElement>
public class CourseDBElement extends Object implements Comparable<CourseDBElement>
This class represents an element in a course database. It stores information about a course, including the course ID, CRN (Course Registration Number), credits, room number, and instructor name. It implements the Comparable interface for comparing elements based on CRN.
